Name: Treadmill
Description: We have 4 Treadmills in our gym and they have a lot of settings. They are really easy to be used both by beginners and advanced.

Name: Upper Chest Machine
Description: We have two upper chest machines which can be loaded with a lot of heavy weights.

Name: Down Chest Machine
Description: We have two machines for the down side of the chest. They are really easy to use and it can be load with a lot of heavy weight.

Name: Bench Press
Description: We have 4 bench presses and a lot of weights to be put on them. There are 10 bars you can use

Name: Leg Press
Description: We have 2 leg presses that can be loaded with a lot of heavy weights. It is really easy to be used by beginners and advanced.

Name: Cross Trainer
Description: We have 4 cross trainers. It can be used simultaniouly by 4 people a lot of settings and easy for use.

Name: Bicycle
Description: We have 4 bicycles in our gym. It has eassy settings and burns a lot of calories.

Name: Gladiators
Description: We have two gladiators. They are really powerfull and many people can use it. It is for strong people.

Name: Karate Room
Description: Our karate room has many bags and two rings. It is wide and you can do many exercises.

Name: Boxing Room
Description: Our boxing room is really big and has five rings with twenty bags. You can use it freely.
